Package main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Action
    Listens to various keys pressed and then adds said keypresses into the View class.
    Controller
    Controls the state of the game with the View class passing messages to the controller.
    Main
    Main class
    Model
    Model class stores information about the current game such as lives, score, the field, and position/state of both the ball and paddle.
    View
    View class contains the GUI and input for the game.
